nodes.text: Dash-1044, nicknamed "Four-Four," was a clone trooper who served in the Grand Army of the Republic during the Clone Wars.

Around 21 BBY, Dash-1044 took part in a mission to the planet Malastare. He was killed by primitive Dug warriors. Dash-1044, nicknamed "Four-Four," was a clone trooper who served in a mission to Malastare during the Clone Wars. He was found dead.
